text: Nicholas Perry (born May 19, 1992) is a Ukrainian-born American Internet celebrity. He is known as Nikocado Avocado on YouTube. , he has over 7 million subscribers and 1.8 billion views on 6 YouTube channels. His "hook" is mukbang videos.
